### Health
GET http://localhost:3001/api/health

###

### Login
# @name login
POST http://localhost:3001/api/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "race-pass-1"
}

###

### Current user
GET http://localhost:3001/api/sessions/current
Cookie: {{login.response.headers.Set-Cookie}}

###

### Full network
GET http://localhost:3001/api/network/full
Cookie: {{login.response.headers.Set-Cookie}}

###

### Start game
POST http://localhost:3001/api/games
Cookie: {{login.response.headers.Set-Cookie}}

###

### Login without loading network first
# @name loginWithoutNetwork
POST http://localhost:3001/api/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "bruno@example.com",
  "password": "race-pass-2"
}

###

### Start game without network, expected 409
POST http://localhost:3001/api/games
Cookie: {{loginWithoutNetwork.response.headers.Set-Cookie}}

###

### Logout
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/sessions/current
Cookie: {{login.response.headers.Set-Cookie}}
